           perform   cmp-sng-fld-000      thru cmp-sng-fld-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riciclo                                     *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     exe-exp-cdp-620.
       exe-exp-cdp-630.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ciclo di scansione                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
       exe-exp-cdp-640.
           add       1                    to   w-exe-ctr-001          .
           if        w-exe-ctr-001        >    03
                     go to exe-exp-cdp-650.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Flag non bloccanti                          *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "A "                 to   w-scr-str-tip          .
           move      rf-cdp-flg-nbx
                    (w-exe-ctr-001)       to   w-scr-str-ele          .
           move      01                   to   w-scr-lun-ele          .
           perform   cmp-sng-fld-000      thru cmp-sng-fld-999        .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * S-e-p-a-r-a-t-o-r-i                         *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
